@startuml Secuencia de Login
!theme plain
actor Usuario
participant "Frontend\n(React)" as Frontend
participant "API REST" as API
participant "Security\nFilter" as Security
participant "AuthService" as Service
database "MySQL" as DB

Usuario -> Frontend: Ingresa credenciales
Frontend -> API: POST /auth/login\n{username, password}
API -> Security: Valida request
Security -> Service: authenticate()
Service -> DB: SELECT usuario\nWHERE username=?
DB --> Service: Usuario encontrado
Service -> Service: Verificar password\n(BCrypt)
Service -> Service: Generar JWT token
Service --> Security: Token generado
Security --> API: Respuesta con token
API --> Frontend: {token, usuario}
Frontend -> Frontend: Almacenar token\n(localStorage)
Frontend --> Usuario: Login exitoso

@enduml
